<i>adjective</i>: 치렁치렁하다 [치렁치렁하다] <i>noun</i>: 미행 [미행] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>치렁치렁하다 [치렁치렁하다]</dt><br>
<dd>trailing; drooping</dd><br>
<dd>아래로 길게 늘어진 천이나 물건이 부드럽게 처져 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>A cloth or object hung down swaying here and there smoothly and repeatedly.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>미행 [미행]</dt><br>
<dd>trailing; shadowing</dd><br>
<dd>감시하거나 증거를 잡기 위하여 남의 뒤를 몰래 따라감.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of secretly following someone in order to keep an eye on him/her or get evidence.</dd><br>
</li>
